# Pytest ReRun

Re-run only changed files in specified branch

# Install

```bash
pip install git+https://github.com/zeburek/pytest-rerun
```

# Run

```bash
pytest --only-changed --rerun-main-branch="origin/master" --rerun-diff-branch="current"
```

